Well, I started this project exactly a year ago.  And I just need these 2 more.  I couldn't even imagine going after the entire set.  I will admit, I don't look for these cards all the time, but still, not an easy thing to do.  Down to my last 2.
Well, another year gone by and still looking for these last 2.  Also going for a 52 Topps Mantle now.  Crazy :)
It's been a long time.  Still need one more!
